g.title: j927399648
g.text: Hypothetical question: If I wanted to ask you out for drinks, would I end up with stitches?

g.title: j3801373262
g.text: But I don't drink, never have
You'll have to be more creative to get into my pants
Or whatever it is I have to wear now

g.title: j79841389
g.text: Good to know. :) Any hints on what I can do to win you over, then?

g.title: j597667419
g.text: On that topic, do you... I've been meaning to ask...

g.title: j369287667
g.text: You just should be real certain that you know what you're for, babas
If you like it sweet and gentle go talk to Aoi or Amir
I am too used to pain and like it too much for that kind of thing

g.title: j3928054913
g.text: Um... Yeah, never mind. Pain's not really my thing.

g.title: j3977279939
g.text: I've been curious if you and the other protoframes still had... y'know... your... y'know... parts...

g.title: j2247822972
g.text: You can't just ASK people what they -
Aaaay babaaaaassss I have not laughed so hard in a looooong time

g.title: j994907621
g.text: You can let me know if you change your mind

g.title: j2691616004
g.text: Think you can take it, do you?

g.title: j1504995206
g.text: Maybe if you are a good little babas
You just might find out, mm?
If you like it sweet and gentle go talk to Aoi or Amir
I am too used to pain and like it too much for that kind of thing

g.title: j2985394125
g.text: Can't be daydreaming when I've got work to do
